        {
            "id": 6132908,
            "title": "外資趁台股攻頂連四賣 賣超86億元砍面板雙虎及金融股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (29) 日上沖下洗，盤中衝上 24570.15 點新高後拉回，收盤翻黑下跌 3.35 點收在最低 24233.1 點，外資賣超 86.35 億元、連 4 賣，其中大砍面板雙虎共近 3.2 萬張，以及多檔金融股，反手買超宏達電 1.57 萬張最多。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6132908/l/f6afd0df0fdcebd74ab2cfb6344115f6.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">外資趁台股攻頂連四賣 賣超86億元砍面板雙虎及金融股。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超面板雙虎群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>) 近 1.72 萬張、友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)1.47 萬張，以及欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)1.01 萬張等電子股，傳產則賣超南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)1.18 萬張、陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)9174 張、長榮航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2618-TW</a>)8663 張。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資也賣超多檔金融股，包括中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)1.67 萬張、第一金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2892:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2892\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2892-TW</a>)1.26 萬張、富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>)1.21 萬張、凱基金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2883-TW</a>)1.16 萬張、台新新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)9228 張、以及彰銀 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2801:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2801\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2801-TW</a>)、遠東銀 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2845:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2845\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2845-TW</a>) 各逾 8800 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資買超前幾名多為電子股，最多的是宏達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2498:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2498\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2498-TW</a>)1.57 萬張、再來有日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)8183 張、華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)7255 張、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2371-TW</a>)6944 張等，傳產則有鋼鐵指標大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>)5782 張以及中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)4981 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，外資也買超漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>)6684 張，以及重電股士電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1503:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1503\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1503-TW</a>)5426 張、中興電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1513:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1513\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1513-TW</a>)5204 張，金融股以華南金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2880:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2880\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2880-TW</a>)4789 張較多，ETF 最多的則為元大滬深 300 正 2 1.16 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
