ews_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6591\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6591-TW</a>)、劍麟 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2228:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2228\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2228-TW</a>)、機器人概念股上緯投 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3708:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3708\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3708-TW</a>)、邦泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8935:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8935\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8935-TW</a>)、聰泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5474:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5474\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5474-TW</a>)、連接器貿聯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3665:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3665\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3665-TW</a>)、半導體測試介面穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>)、晶圓測試卡精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、半導體設備旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)、電子零件中探針 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6217:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6217\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6217-TW</a>)、先進封測京元電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>)、利機 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3444:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3444\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3444-TW</a>)、以及軍供概念股晟田 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4541:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4541\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4541-TW</a>)、龍德造 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6753:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6753\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6753-TW</a>)、IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)、漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>)、宏齊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6168:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6168\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6168-TW</a>)、合勤控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3704:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3704\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3704-TW</a>)、為升 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2231-TW</a>)… 等，近期個股表現就是相對犀利，只要你懂得做把握，真的會賺很大！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今天不管你是否要加入我們的會員家族，觀察我們一段時間的好朋友，一定都相當清楚，我採取的選股邏輯為「即先選產業再挑好股」，把未來看好的產業先挑出來，再從裡面挑出第一名的好股，事後證明我們的動作是對的；繼 PCB 楠梓電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2316:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2316-TW</a>) 翻倍大賺、數位雲端智通 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8932:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8932\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8932-TW</a>)波段最高價差逾 + 90%、AI 伺服器龍頭鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 波段價差也逾 + 35% 之後，近期陸續鎖定的股票，不論是機器人概念股聰泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5474:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5474\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5474-TW</a>) 及自動化設備迅得 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6438:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6438\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6438-TW</a>) 等持續大漲再創新高、機器人概念股邦泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8935:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8935\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8935-TW</a>) 及 PCB 瀚宇博 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5469:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5469\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5469-TW</a>) 等強勢亮燈漲停板，恭喜大家！你們都是最棒的！疾風知勁草板蕩識誠臣，如果你想突破現況一定要動起來，該換的、該買的、該調整的，直接採取行動讓一切都變成可能。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>珍惜所託真心照顧</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大師兄只堅持做對的事，9 月翻倍飆股行情正要開始，多頭架構穩固不必預設高點，現在的行情不需要去追漲高的，要買進資金剛要流入的族群，現在這種盤空手者別緊張，接下來還有更多飆股會被點火，關鍵是你想做哪一種？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新題材、籌碼乾淨剛起漲</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人鎖定、業績撐腰賺波段</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>從明天開始不管你前面有沒有賺，這裡就是你全新的起跑點，八月完美收尾，下一步跟著我買在大漲噴出前，九月財富特快車，做對股票真的會賺很快，聯絡我【輕鬆上車】立刻把握，先登記滿意再辦理</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://forms.gle/yLSyWWKa9xPtg8va8\">https://forms.gle/yLSyWWKa9xPtg8va8</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6132943/l/570fbc48a357453132a23b387a8abd04.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6132943/l/0e6363624b1aaac486bc3b1640415a09.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6132943/l/ff746a71067c3424e441db6236d3776d.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><div class=\"youtube-embed-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;padding-top:30px;height:0;overflow:hidden;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/o_3yxgBhTjU\" style=\"position: absolute;top: 0;left: 0;width: 100%;height: 100%;\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>工商時報績效競賽 13 冠王、卓越績效傲視同業、專業實力有目共賭！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>更多第一手訊息、以及飆股機會→請加入大師兄飆股鑫天地的大家族</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>LINE@連結網址：<a href=\"https://line.me/R/ti/p/@gold99\">https://line.me/R/ti/p/%40gold99</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Telegram 連結網址：<a href=\"https://t.me/gold0999\">https://t.me/gold0999</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>諮詢專線︰02-23219933(24 小時專人服務)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6132943/l/a33fa27c65d95128884513d313e1f60d.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>文章來源：倫元投顧陳學進分析師</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\">本公司所推薦分析之個別有價證券<br/>\n無不當之財務利益關係 以往之績效不保證未來獲利<br/>\n投資人應獨立判斷 審慎評估並自負投資風險</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
